<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qtquickcontrols-index.xml">Qt Quick Controls</db:link> provides QML types for creating user interfaces. These QML types work in conjunction with <db:link xlink:href="qtquick-index.xml">Qt Quick</db:link> and <db:link xlink:href="qtquicklayouts-index.xml">Qt Quick Layouts</db:link>.</db:para>
<db:para>Qt Quick Controls QML types can be imported into your application using the following import statement in your .qml file:</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="qml">import QtQuick.Controls
</db:programlisting>
